Reclusa::

"Did I here you say clone?" She thought about this. "Hhmmm, No. I do
not think so. Any more of me around here and I'll be too busy in my
own private war. Then Hydrus will never see just how wonderful your
work really is. But perhaps, we cold clone other soilders and give
them the same up grades you gave me. Spiders are not known for geting
along with one another."
